{"tid":2085664,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"做多好定做少好","createTime":"2020-06-30T03:40:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T12:18:21.000Z","uid":247247,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"09f414c01668324ceb323d1bf4100fba78166b7b","tid":2085664,"uid":247247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T03:40:02.000Z","msg":"老細有時找你幫手做嘢 究竟做多好定做少好<br />\n閪工唔使咁上心 不過呢度當住老細係正常人先 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做多好 <br />\n老細找你幫手仲唔係上位既好機會 冇得升都博加下人工<br />\n同埋反正都要做 不如做多少少表演下自己能幹既一面又可以幫到老細手<br />\n如果之後有手尾跟都唔使番手做得咁辛苦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔使做咁多  <br />\n老細要ABC咪俾ABC佢囉 咁多事做咩<br />\n好似去食飯咁 我要咖喱腩咪俾咖喱腩我囉 我唔使聽咩是日精選<br />\n同埋香港效率行先 快手快腳做完好過"},{"pid":"5bfe02a1a9d104bce5d1d5c9e2cf1e070c9a25f4","tid":2085664,"uid":12158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T03:40:43.000Z","msg":"香港搞成咁仲上位都唔知有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f689218c810f6c8a70fa8fda287ce1a7cb7aa2e1","tid":2085664,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T03:44:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">7一維園見</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9vzHhbe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9vzHhbe.jpg&h=c0777e33&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HXtg54z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHXtg54z.jpg&h=eae3d5c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qizj3Rf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQizj3Rf.jpg&h=d33e105b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sg0OXbk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSg0OXbk.jpg&h=791a8ec6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ivfSEpG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.c